# Yocto build directories created by bsp-setup.sh or manual oe-init-build-env runs
**/build/
**/build-*/

# Download and shared-state caches
**/downloads/
**/downloads-*/
**/sstate-cache/
**/sstate-cache-*/

# Common build output directories inside Yocto build trees
**/tmp/
**/tmp-*/
**/cache/
**/stamps/
**/deploy/
**/buildhistory/

# BitBake runtime artifacts
**/bitbake-cookerdaemon.log
**/bitbake.lock
**/pn-buildlist
**/task-depends.dot
**/package-depends.dot

# Generated environment helper from local builds
**/SOURCE_THIS


# Python bytecode and virtual environments
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/

# Common local editor and OS artifacts
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store